Package: modFrames
Title: Frame Analysis and Creative Journey Storytelling Module
Version: 0.7.11
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Bobby",
           family = "Fatemi",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bobby@artalytics.app")
Description: Shiny UI module for the Artalytics platform providing frame
    comparison, timelapse playback, and AI-powered creative journey
    storytelling. Enables side-by-side frame analysis with difference
    visualization, animated timelapse progression, and marketing-ready
    narrative insights about artwork creation process. Designed to be
    embedded in appPlatform, not deployed standalone.
